---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Growth Marketing Canvas™ — Leverage a full‑funnel growth strategy"
  description="Define a 12‑month actionable, customer‑centric growth plan. Used by 2,000+ companies worldwide. Download the Growth Marketing Canvas and align your team around what moves the needle."
  ogImage="/images/Growth-marketing-canvas_A1_V19_thumbnail.webp"
  canonical="https://www.growthmarketingcanvas.com/"
>
  <!-- TOP BANNER -->
  <section
    id="top-banner"
    class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 to-orange-500 text-white"
  >
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-4 sm:py-5">
      <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">
        The Growth Marketing Canvas<sup class="align-super text-[0.6em]">™</sup
        >
      </p>

      <p class="mt-1 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-300">
        Leverage the power of a full-funnel growth strategy
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section id="hero" aria-label="Hero" class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-orange-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5">
      <div class="grid items-center gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
            The Growth Marketing Canvas<sup class="align-super text-base"
              >™</sup
            >
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
            A simple, battle‑tested framework to turn endless ideas into a
            focused 12‑month growth plan — built with your team, for your
            customers.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
            <a
              href="/files/Growth-marketing-canvas_A1_V19.pdf"
              download
              class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-orange-500 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow hover:bg-orange-600 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-400"
            >
              Download the Canvas
            </a>
            <a
              href="#how-it-works"
              class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-gray-100 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-300"
            >
              See how it works
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
            Downloaded <strong>56k+ times</strong> · Loved by marketers and product
            teams
          </p>
        </div>
        <figure class="order-first lg:order-last">
          <img
            src="/images/Growth-marketing-canvas_A1_V19_thumbnail.webp"
            alt="Preview of the Growth Marketing Canvas"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow"
          />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LOGOS / SOCIAL PROOF (uses a combined logos image for now) -->
  <section id="logos" aria-label="Trusted by" class="py-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5">
      <p
        class="text-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500"
      >
        Used by 2,000+ companies across the globe
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-center">
        <img
          src="/images/GMC-customer-logos-4-1-e1557141622357.webp"
          alt="Customer logos"
          class="h-14 w-auto opacity-80 sm:h-16 md:h-20"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM / PROMISE -->
  <section id="why" aria-label="Why the Canvas" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 grid items-center gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
          Ambitious growth is hard. The Canvas makes it doable.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
          When ideas are infinite, teams stall. The Growth Marketing Canvas
          focuses your efforts on what customers truly need and aligns
          stakeholders around a single, testable roadmap. No fluff — just a
          clear path to sustainable growth.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-gray-800">
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold">Customer‑centric:</span> start from pains,
            jobs, and moments that matter.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold">Team‑powered:</span> harness collective intelligence
            to surface better ideas.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="font-semibold">Actionable:</span> prioritize experiments
            that move acquisition, activation, retention, and revenue.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <figure>
        <img
          src="/images/DSC0065.webp"
          alt="Team using the Growth Marketing Canvas in a workshop"
          class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow"
        />
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section id="how-it-works" aria-label="How it works" class="py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
        How it works
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-8 grid items-start gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <ol class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-1 lg:order-2">
          <li class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Run a process‑driven workshop</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
              Map your funnel, expose bottlenecks, and frame problems worth
              solving with crisp success metrics.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">
              Align your team around one plan
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
              Gather input from product, marketing, sales, and success. Build
              shared context and pick owners.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">
              Prioritize high‑leverage experiments
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
              Brainstorm, score, and schedule ideas that move the funnel. Learn
              fast, iterate faster.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <figure class="lg:order-1">
          <img
            src="/images/DSC0125.webp"
            alt="Workshop in progress"
            class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow"
          />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section id="testimonials" aria-label="Testimonials" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5">
      <h2
        class="text-center text-3xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl"
      >
        LOVED BY OUR COMMUNITY
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-8 grid items-stretch gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <figure class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <blockquote class="text-lg">
            “Wonderful tool to structure your ideation process when designing
            your growth strategy.”
          </blockquote>
          <figcaption
            class="mt-auto flex items-center gap-3 pt-4 text-sm text-gray-600"
          >
            <img
              src="/images/Noemie-Benoit-Circle.webp"
              alt="Noémie Benoit"
              class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full object-cover"
            />
            <span
              ><span class="font-semibold">Noémie Benoit</span> — CMO, Around Media</span
            >
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <blockquote class="text-lg">
            “Eazl thinks highly enough of MAD Kings’ Growth Marketing Canvas to
            offer it to all of the aspiring growth hackers in our community.”
          </blockquote>
          <figcaption
            class="mt-auto flex items-center gap-3 pt-4 text-sm text-gray-600"
          >
            <img
              src="/images/Davis-Jones-Circle.webp"
              alt="Davis Jones"
              class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full object-cover"
            />
            <span
              ><span class="font-semibold">Davis Jones</span> — CEO, Eazl</span
            >
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AUTHORS -->
  <section id="authors" aria-label="About the authors" class="py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
        About the authors
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <article
          class="flex items-start gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 p-6"
        >
          <div class="flex w-20 shrink-0 flex-col items-center gap-2">
            <img
              src="/images/Jean-Christophe-Cuvelier-circle.webp"
              alt="Jean‑Christophe Cuvelier"
              class="h-20 w-20 aspect-square rounded-full object-cover"
            />
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/totophe/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 ring-1 ring-inset ring-blue-200 transition hover:bg-blue-100 hover:text-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400"
              aria-label="Jean‑Christophe Cuvelier on LinkedIn"
              title="LinkedIn"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="currentColor"
                class="h-5 w-5"
                aria-hidden="true"
              >
                <path
                  d="M19 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2ZM8.339 18.338H6V9.75h2.339v8.588ZM7.169 8.669a1.356 1.356 0 1 1 0-2.713 1.356 1.356 0 0 1 0 2.713ZM18.338 18.338H16v-4.41c0-1.053-.02-2.406-1.466-2.406-1.468 0-1.693 1.146-1.693 2.33v4.486H10.5V9.75h2.244v1.17h.032c.313-.594 1.08-1.218 2.225-1.218 2.381 0 2.838 1.568 2.838 3.607v5.029Z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="sr-only">LinkedIn</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Jean‑Christophe Cuvelier</h3>

            <p class="mt-1 text-gray-700">
              JC is a jack‑of‑all‑trades, data‑driven growth leader and AI
              expert. He blends marketing, product, and engineering to turn
              insights into execution—automating workflows and building systems
              that scale. Today, he helps teams leverage AI to accelerate
              acquisition, activation, and retention— without the hype. He
              mentors founders and enjoys turning messy go‑to‑market puzzles
              into simple, testable plans.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article
          class="flex items-start gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 p-6"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/Thomas-Paris_Circle.webp"
            alt="Thomas Paris"
            class="h-20 w-20 rounded-full object-cover"
          />
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Thomas Paris</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-gray-700">
              Thomas is a growth marketer and co‑founder of MAD Kings and
              Pictawall. He champions customer‑centric, data‑driven
              experimentation as the shortest path to traction and revenue.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DOWNLOAD -->
  <section
    id="download"
    aria-label="Download the Canvas"
    class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-white"
  >
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
        Get your Growth Marketing Canvas
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">A1 printable PDF · Free download</p>
      <a
        href="/files/Growth-marketing-canvas_A1_V19.pdf"
        download
        class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center rounded-2xl bg-orange-500 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white shadow-lg hover:bg-orange-600 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-orange-300"
      >
        Download PDF
      </a>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
        872 KB · print‑ready · instant access
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section id="faq" aria-label="FAQ" class="py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-5">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
        Frequently asked questions
      </h2>
      <div
        class="mt-6 divide-y divide-gray-200 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200"
      >
        <details class="group p-5 open:pb-4">
          <summary
            class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between text-lg font-medium"
            >What is included in the download?<span
              class="ml-4 text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180">▾</span
            ></summary
          >
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
            An A1 printable PDF of the Growth Marketing Canvas with usage tips.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="group p-5">
          <summary
            class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between text-lg font-medium"
            >Who is it for?<span
              class="ml-4 text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180">▾</span
            ></summary
          >
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
            Growth leaders, product managers, and marketers who need a focused
            plan.
          </p>
        </details>
        <details class="group p-5">
          <summary
            class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between text-lg font-medium"
            >Can I use it with my team?<span
              class="ml-4 text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180">▾</span
            ></summary
          >
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
            Yes. It’s designed for collaborative workshops online or in person.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER NOTE -->
  <section id="site-note" class="bg-orange-500 py-10 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 text-center">
      <p>
        © 2017–{new Date().getFullYear()} The Growth Marketing Canvas · By
        <a
          href="https://www.madkings.com/"
          rel="noopener"
          class="underline underline-offset-2">MAD Kings</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
